{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "980e7aee-4e6e-4119-9c7c-b34d98612bab", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/980e7aee-4e6e-4119-9c7c-b34d98612bab@1.pkg/1772597584822/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597585549", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/980e7aee-4e6e-4119-9c7c-b34d98612bab@1.pkg/1772597584822/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597585549"}, "identifier": "980e7aee-4e6e-4119-9c7c-b34d98612bab", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>D:零售业属于非公有制经济，国务院印发《提振消费专项行动方案》，为零售行业注入发展新动能，是国家为提振消费需求制定的宏观调控政策，故D符合题意;</p>\n\n<p>A:国务院印发《提振消费专项行动方案》并不是法律，不能为提升竞争力、打造消费品牌提供法律保障，故A说法错误;</p>\n\n<p>B:题文中体现的是政府的作用，没有体现市场机制的作用，故B说法与题不符;</p>\n\n<p>C:国有经济是国民经济的主导力量，零售业属于非公有制经济，故C说法错误;</p>\n\n<p>故本题选D。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>(原创)2025年《政府工作报告》将“大力提振消费”作为首要任务，2025年3月16日中共中央办公厅、国务院办公厅印发了《提振消费专项行动方案》，为零售行业注入发展新动能。出台《提振消费专项行动方案》（&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "(原创)2025年《政府工作报告》将“大力提振消费”作为首要任务，2025年3月16日中共中央办公厅、国务院办公厅印发了《提振消费专项行动方案》，为零售行业注入发展新动能。出台《提振消费专项行动方案》（  ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/980e7aee-4e6e-4119-9c7c-b34d98612bab@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754817893583", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>为提升竞争力、打造消费品牌提供法律保障</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>体现了市场机制在资源配置中的决定性作用</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>将促进作为国民经济主导力量的零售业发展</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>是国家为提振消费需求制定的宏观调控政策</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>(原创)2025年《政府工作报告》将“大力提振消费”作为首要任务，2025年3月16日中共中央办公厅、国务院办公厅印发了《提振消费专项行动方案》，为零售行业注入发展新动能。出台《提振消费专项行动方案》（&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "980e7aee-4e6e-4119-9c7c-b34d98612bab", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "(原创)2025年《政府工作报告》将“大力提振消费”作为首要任务，2025年3月16日中共中央办公厅、国务院办公厅印发了《提振消费专项行动方案》，为零售行业注入发展新动能。出台《提振消费专项行动方案》（  ）"}, "global_description": {"